    public class TimeChartDataSet
extends GenericSplitSetPlot
implements org.jfree.data.xy.IntervalXYDataset, org.jfree.data.xy.TableXYDataset, org.jfree.data.xy.XYDomainInfo, org.jfree.data.xy.XYRangeInfo
    A GenericSplitSetPlot that implements the appropriate JFreeChart interfaces. We implement IntervalXYDataset to represent the actual time periods so the data can be plotted as bar-chart and return the middle of the period as the data point.
